    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies fully serviced. This example boasts a factory-spec Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a documented reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's primary known weak point. The variable M differential lock remains tight, and the suspension geometry is perfectly dialed for track-inspired turn-in without sacrificing street composure. Every seal, bushing, and mechanical component reflects a meticulous maintenance history. This is a turn-key, collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
