    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented here is an automotive specimen of the highest caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, mirroring its original showroom state in every discernible detail. Meticulously maintained and preserved with the utmost care, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. We invite you to inspect this standard-setting example firsthand.",
      "price": 44900.0,
