    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s in absolute pristine condition and honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally babied, kept super clean inside and out, and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Don't miss out on a ride this clean, it's ready for a new home!",
